{"tid":1209983,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係一個幼師 以後唔知點同我啲學生講 警察叔叔係幫手捉壞人","createTime":"2019-06-12T12:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-19T10:42:11.000Z","uid":213837,"like":223,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"1cabcddee95bdd2012ec4aeb26e48a6f670a1e85","tid":1209983,"uid":213837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:46:43.000Z","msg":"今日我罷左工 請左假 去左幫手, 見證住啲警察使用暴力對待我地呢啲手無手無寸鐵既市民 , 甚至傾緊電話 幫手搬水 可以比二十幾個警察圍打。<br />\n我真係唔知點同我啲小朋友講, 警察係正義 係幫手捉壞人, 亦都好唔想聽到佢地既夢想係做警察,即使佢地真係想做警察 希望二十年後既佢地同以家呢班垃圾唔同。<br />\n<br />\n各位 今日辛苦曬, 香港人繼續努力。"},{"pid":"0f32554bf9883e37bc3595fd4067fa5c65a613b4","tid":1209983,"uid":182770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:47:48.000Z","msg":"警察叔的變壞了"},{"pid":"e6f0941e12a697b16fafd6cf50f14cb8a83d943a","tid":1209983,"uid":148987,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:48:03.000Z","msg":"呢d唔係警察<br />\n係爪牙"},{"pid":"2c551ec63ba56ab181edae9aab77bf8d6872c7c2","tid":1209983,"uid":212704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:48:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0b8924ecd5847ee383817d8c0282a52313e36f","tid":1209983,"uid":126947,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"我已經直接教小朋友警察係壞人<br />\n蝦啲好人哥哥姐姐"},{"pid":"527cda1c6a48a09db65d85d84e9d2d9bcaaa9e2f","tid":1209983,"uid":213837,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7e0b8924ecd5847ee383817d8c0282a52313e36f","tid":1209983,"uid":126947,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:48:14.000Z","msg":"我已經直接教小朋友警察係壞人<br />\n蝦啲好人哥哥姐姐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"唉 好希望佢地新一代唔會係咁"},{"pid":"6429c6d6af073a9620b990ed8db380cb74ac3d78","tid":1209983,"uid":213837,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T12:49:46.000Z","msg":"佢地仲細 咩都唔識"},{"pid":"9c0bc977b131cedf1dc7b2d545b854a84d551413","tid":12099